  <div class="main">
    <div class = "topDescription">
      <div class="imgIcon"><img src="../images/icons/top_icon.png"></div>
      <p>
        Hello, I'm a software developer located in Taiwan.
        I'm passionate about building web and mobile applications.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="projectGrid" id="projects">
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <div class="projectCard">
        <div class="img"><img src="../images/projects/tsp_solver.png"></div>
        <div class="cardContent">
            <h3>TSP solver for Final Fantasy</h3>
            <p>
                A full-stack web application that parses in-game logs and calculates the fastest route.
                The algorithm accounts for multiple starting points, such as teleports, to optimize the path efficiently.
            </p>
            <a href="ff/optimalRoute" class="ffRouteCalculatorRef">Live app</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="projectCard">
        <div class="img"><img src="../images/projects/fitsy.png"></div>
        <div class="cardContent">
             <h3>New-gen menu generator</h3>
             <p>
                Fitsy is a cross-platform mobile app that generates AI powered meal plans in seconds.
                It automatically calculates the optimal daily calorie intake based on the user’s lifestyle and goals.
             </p>
             <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fitsy.fitsy" class="ffRouteCalculatorRef">
                Download on Google Play
             </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="projectCard">
        <div class="img"><img src="../images/projects/overlay_translator.png"></div>
        <div class="cardContent">
            <h3>Overlay Translator</h3>
            <p>
              A lightweight desktop translator with image-to-text (OCR) recognition.
              It supports customizable global hotkeys for quickly selecting areas on the screen.
            </p>
            <a href="https://github.com/VictoriaTaiwan/OverlayTranslator/releases" class="overlayTranslatorRef">
              Download on Github
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      </div>

    <div id="about" class="aboutMe">
        <p>
        I'm a mobile and full-stack web developer with a strong interest in cross-platform technologies
        and user-friendly design. I’m passionate about Flutter for mobile development, and I enjoy building
        reliable backend services with Spring Boot and responsive web applications with Angular.
        </p>
    </div>

